Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI.utils

Class IslandPrinter

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.CLI.utils.IslandPrinter
public class IslandPrinter extends Object
IslandPrinter role is to create every single island box, after the creation all the created boxes are reunited by a single grid map by IslandMapPrinter

    • getIsland

      public String[][] getIsland(int islandIndex, boolean isPresent, Integer numTowers, TowerType type, Integer[] islandStudent, int numNoEntryTiles)
      Returns the completed island box of the island that have specified id. The method filled the island skeleton with the dynamics part of the island
      Parameters:
      islandIndex - the id of the island
      isPresent - boolean value for reporting if mother nature is present in the island
      numTowers - number of towers present into the island
      type - type of tower present into the island
      islandStudent - array containing the number of students for each type
      numNoEntryTiles - number of no_entry_tile present in the island
      Returns:
      the completed island box of the island that have specified id
